  "extras": {
    "impact_clause": "An act to amend the Budget Act of 2023 (Chapters 12, 38, and 189 of the Statutes of 2023) by amending Sections 19.564 and 39.10 of that act, to amend the Budget Act of 2024 (Chapters 22, 35, and 994 of the Statutes of 2024) by amending Items 3125-101-6093 and 6100-488 of Section 2.00 of, and amending Section 39.10 of, that act, and to amend the Budget Act of 2025 (Chapters 4 and 5 of the Statutes of 2025) by amending Items 0250-494, 0509-101-0001, 0540-103-0001, 1700-001-0001, 3125-102-6093, 3360-001-3228, 3360-101-3228, 3480-001-0890, 3540-001-0001, 3540-101-0890, 3760-101-0001, 3790-003-6093, 3790-101-0516, 3790-102-6093, 3900-001-0115, 3900-001-3359, 4260-116-3397, 6100-134-0890, 6120-011-0001, 7600-001-0004, 7600-001-3418, 7760-101-0001, and 8570-001-6093 of, adding Items 3100-001-0890, 3540-002-6093, 3560-101-6093, and 6120-217-0001 to, and repealing Items 1700-101-0001, 3540-102-6093, and 3720-101-0001 of, Section 2.00 of,\n\t amending Sections 39.00, 39.10, and 99.50 of, and adding Section 15.01 to, that act, relating to the state budget, and making an appropriation therefor, to take effect immediately, budget bill.",
